# Committed on purpose. PUBLIC_* vars are inlined into the browser bundle at
# build time, so this is public by definition — it is the widget's site key,
# not its secret. The matching TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY lives in the encrypted
# secrets store and is only ever read server-side by form-api.
#
# This has to be committed rather than supplied by the deploy secret: without
# it the build renders no widget, no token is sent, and form-api rejects every
# submission as spam. The form fails closed.
PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=0x4AAAAAACxr51WYc4ZRzmRX
